課程教材 Course Material
	    1.自編教材    

參考書目 References
	    1.American College of Sports Medicine. (2009). American College of Sports Medicine position stand. Progression models in resistance training for healthy adults. Medicine and Science in Sports and Exercise, 41, 687.
